Discworld ritual help
Calm

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Calm - Calms your enemies.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The Calm ritual allows you to calm monsters down.  Calming enemies down means that they stop fighting you.  The success of this ritual is based upon your skill in faith.rituals.defensive and the target's resistance.
.EP